OL,3,CMan jailed for posting threatening
OL,4,Cmessages towards Derry Mayor
OL,6,FA man has been jailed at Derry
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court for posting
OL,8,Fthreatening messages towards the Mayor
OL,9,Fof the city, Councillor Lillian Senoi
OL,10,FBarr.
OL,12,FKevin Barry McIntyre, who is 31 and of
OL,13,FMiller Street in Derry, had been
OL,14,Fconvicted of two counts of sending
OL,15,Fmessages of a 'menacing nature' on May
OL,16,F2 and May 4 last year.
