OL,3,CMan jailed for posting threatening
OL,4,Cmessages towards Derry Mayor
OL,6,FThe court heard that the post about
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's first black Mayor
OL,8,Fwas headed 'terrorist alert' and said
OL,9,FCouncillor Senoi Barr would be removed
OL,10,Ffrom the city 'dead or alive'.
OL,12,FHe was interviewed by police on May 5
OL,13,Fand responded that 'everyone leaves
OL,14,FDerry dead or alive'.
OL,16,FHe denied making threats and said that
OL,17,Fwas simply one interpretation of the
OL,18,Fmessages.
