OL,3,CMan jailed for posting threatening
OL,4,Cmessages towards Derry Mayor
OL,6,FDefence counsel Michael Donaghey said
OL,7,Fhis client had always accepted he had
OL,8,Fposted the comments but maintained
OL,9,Fthat he did not intend to put anyone
OL,10,Fin fear.
OL,12,FHe said the messages were posted on
OL,13,FMcIntyre's own social media account
OL,14,Fand there had been no direct contact.
OL,16,FThe barrister said that perhaps the
OL,17,Fdefendant had learned a lesson and
OL,18,Fsuggested a community service sentence.
OL,20,FJudge McElholm said: "I wouldn't
OL,21,Finflict this man on the community."
