OL,3,CMan jailed for posting threatening
OL,4,Cmessages towards Derry Mayor
OL,6,FHe said the posts were 'offensive' and
OL,7,Fthen in his pre-sentence report
OL,8,FMcIntyre claimed the Mayor was racist
OL,9,Fagainst the people of Derry.
OL,11,FThe judge also highlighted posts about
OL,12,Fthe MP for Foyle Colum Eastwood where
OL,13,FMcIntyre said he was responsible for
OL,14,Fdeaths due to the Covid vaccine.
OL,16,FJudge McElholm said McIntyre 'deserves
OL,17,Fno consideration from this court nor
OL,18,Fwould he get any'.
